薯片一样裂开。”</p><p>今年早些时候，有人发现他拄着拐杖行走，左膝上裹着冰袋。安萨里后来说，里夫斯在拖车里的地毯上绊倒后膝盖骨骨折。在<em>斯蒂芬·科尔伯特深夜秀中，</em>里夫斯解释了整个故事。 </p><figure id="attachment_3777736" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3777736" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3777736" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/keanu-reeeves-dave-benett-1.jpg" alt="基努·里维斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/keanu-reeeves-dave-benett-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/keanu-reeeves-dave-benett-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/keanu-reeeves-dave-benett-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/keanu-reeeves-dave-benett-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/keanu-reeeves-dave-benett-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/keanu-reeeves-dave-benett-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3777736" class="wp-caption-text">基努·里维斯。图片来源：戴夫·贝内特/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>“我正在与阿齐兹·安萨里和塞斯·罗根一起拍摄一个场景，我们陷入了寒冷之中，”他回忆道。 “我很喜欢它，我站在那里，我们完成了这个场景，你知道什么时候你会感到寒冷并且你会[拖着脚步]吗？我有泳衣和毛巾，你把它套在头上然后进行冷洗？</p><p> “我在这个铺有防护地毯的房间里进行冷洗牌，然后就在这里，就像一个小口袋，我的脚在洗牌时被口袋卡住了，然后我就[倒下]，但是[我的膝盖]没有跟着。</p><p>他继续说道：“然后，我慢慢地摔倒了。我的手臂伸出来，但后来我的膝盖失效了，因为它有一些东西，我用尖刺刺伤了它。我的髌骨——膝盖骨——像薯片一样裂开。”</p><p>在其他地方，里夫斯最近透露，随着 60 岁生日的临近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/keanu-reeves-says-he-thinks-about-death-a-lot-im-59-3777059">，他发现自己经常思考死亡的问题</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/keanu-reeves-signs-with-canadian-hockey-team-for-one-day-3787214">基努·里维斯 (Keanu Reeves) 与加拿大曲棍球队签约一天的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 畅谈 Oasis 为 30 周年再发行而发行的早期《Definitely Maybe》唱片https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-opens-up-about-oasis-early-definitely-maybe-recordings-for-30th-anniversary-reissue-3787210?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel-Gallagher) 提前公开了《绿洲》的 30 周年纪念重新发行录音Surej SinghMon, 26 Aug 2024 05:32:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3787210 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Oasis 1993 年阵容" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>重新发行的内容包括《Live Forever》、《Cigarettes &amp; Drinks》以及近三十年前失踪的更多歌曲的早期版本，将于本周发行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-opens-up-about-oasis-early-definitely-maybe-recordings-for-30th-anniversary-reissue-3787210">Noel Gallagher 发表的有关 Oasis 30 周年纪念再版早期《Definitely Maybe》录音的</a>文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Oasis 1993 年阵容" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a>公开了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>之前闻所未闻的“Definitely Maybe”早期录音——了解更多信息如下。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/every-oasis-song-ranked-greatness-best-worst-2488711">大师列表 - Oasis 录制的每首歌曲均按伟大程度排列</a></strong></li></ul><p>该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-tease-reunion-announcement-after-liam-gallaghers-reading-2024-set-3787128">目前正在预告一些事情</a>，粉丝们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-reunion-tease-one-of-the-most-culturally-significant-events-in-british-history-3787151">认为这将是一次重聚巡演</a>公告， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">他们将于本周五 8 月 30 日发行“Definitely Maybe”30 周年纪念重新发行的早期唱片</a>。</p><p>这些录音（30 年前失踪）来自 Oasis 作为签约乐队的首次录音室录音。在磁带丢失之前，他们在南威尔士的蒙诺谷录音室录制了八首歌曲，最近终于被找回。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c134n75xm17o" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC</em></a>报道，诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 谈到丢失的录音时说道：“我一直说它们不可能失踪，这些录音带一定在某个地方。这些磁带被送到我们的唱片公司后就再也没有出现过。它是罐装的。结果发现它被贴错标签了。所以直到六个月前我才听说过 Monnow Valley 的唱片。” </p><figure id="attachment_3783517" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3783517" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3783517" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher.jpg" alt="绿洲乐队的利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺埃尔·加拉格尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3783517" class="wp-caption-text">绿洲乐队的利亚姆和诺埃尔·加拉格尔。图片来源：凯文·康明斯</figcaption></figure><p>在原始录音丢失后，Oasis 重新录制了这些歌曲并重新混音，最终以“Definitely Maybe”的形式发行。</p><p>周五发布的前所未闻的“失落曲目”包括“Live Forever”、“Cigarettes＆Alcohol”、“Rock &#39;n&#39; Roll Star”、“Shakermaker”和“Columbia”的早期版本。</p><p> 《Definitely Maybe》30 周年纪念版重新发行之际，Oasis 正在本周晚些时候发布一项公告——粉丝们相信这将是一次重聚巡演的公告。昨晚在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">雷丁</a>节上，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)</a>在演出即将结束时在屏幕上调侃了一次神秘约会，据称在“27.08.24”早上 8 点发布了一些消息。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blossoms">Blossoms</a>返校演出之后，同样的图片出现在曼彻斯特， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-tease-reunion-announcement-after-liam-gallaghers-reading-2024-set-3787128">以及演出结束后 Noel、Liam 和 Oasis 的官方 Twitter/X 上</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3776490" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3776490" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3776490" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Noel-and-Liam-Gallagher-posing.jpg" alt="Q 奖 Liam Gallagher 和 Noel Gallagher 与 OASIS、Noel Gallagher、Liam Gallagher 合影（摄影：Mick Hutson/Redferns）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Noel-and-Liam-Gallagher-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Noel-and-Liam-Gallagher-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Noel-and-Liam-Gallagher-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Noel-and-Liam-Gallagher-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Noel-and-Liam-Gallagher-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Noel-and-Liam-Gallagher-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3776490" class="wp-caption-text"> Q 奖 Liam Gallagher 和 Noel Gallagher 与 OASIS、Noel Gallagher、Liam Gallagher 合影（摄影：Mick Hutson/Redferns）</figcaption></figure><p>在雷丁，利亚姆完整地演奏了 Oasis 的首张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">，随后该专辑于 8 月 30 日发行 30 周年纪念再版</a>。而且，为了纪念这一时刻，他花了一点时间大声喊出他的兄弟， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-dedicates-half-the-world-away-to-noel-fucking-gallagher-and-teases-mysterious-date-at-reading-2024-3787108">将《半个世界》献给“诺埃尔他妈的加拉格尔”</a> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-to-oasis-reuniting-for-huge-london-and-manchester-shows-3786823">进一步煽动了绿洲乐队本周五（8月23日）在利兹重聚的谣言。头条设定</a>：“这很有趣吗？我们发现自己处于一个非常有趣的境地。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="绿洲球迷对 2024 年雷丁和利兹重聚巡演传闻做出反应" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UqskhDC6dr0?start=3&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>据传绿洲乐队也有可能成为明年<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>的头条新闻。如果属实，该专辑将在他们 1995 年开创性的 LP“(What&#39;s the Story) Morning Glory?”发行 30 年后推出。</p><p>这些谣言还源于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-praises-liam-in-new-interview-when-i-would-sing-the-song-it-would-sound-good-when-he-would-sing-it-it-would-sound-great-3786196">诺埃尔最近在与约翰·罗伯的谈话中赞扬了利亚姆</a>，他说：“我不会唱《Slide Away》、《香烟和酒精》、《摇滚明星》和《哥伦比亚》等等。 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-opens-up-about-oasis-early-definitely-maybe-recordings-for-30th-anniversary-reissue-3787210">Noel Gallagher 发表的有关 Oasis 30 周年纪念再版早期《Definitely Maybe》录音的</a>文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
